data.description: This impeccably maintained 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, located in the highly sought-after Olsen neighborhood of Amarillo, offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. With its spacious floor plan, abundant natural light, almost brand new plumbing, and a serene master suite with a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom, this home has it all. The backyard oasis beckons you to relax and entertain, while the attached garage provides convenience and storage. Ideal for FHA, VA, and conventional loan buyers looking for a dream home in a prime location. UPDATE: Seller is open to negotiating consessions at $6500+. Don't miss out, schedule your private showing today!
